Dialogue: 0,00:00:27.000,00:00:29.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,Yes. So this is my solution.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:29.000,00:00:34.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,So I do see I get something similar to what I'm supposed to get, right?
Dialogue: 0,00:00:34.000,00:00:40.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,So as things run into the shock wave, this part further flattens and I get a shock wave over here.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:40.000,00:00:46.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,But what about this?
Dialogue: 0,00:00:46.000,00:00:51.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,I have artificially generated oscillations.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:51.000,00:00:56.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,Right. So why is that the case?
Dialogue: 0,00:00:56.000,00:00:59.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,So let's analyze the central flux scheme.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:59.000,00:01:03.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,A little bit more.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:03.000,00:01:10.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,So first of all, one obvious thing we see is that
Dialogue: 0,00:01:10.000,00:01:16.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,it doesn't seem to be conserving or decreasing the
Dialogue: 0,00:01:16.000,00:01:19.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,what's called the total variation, right?
Dialogue: 0,00:01:19.000,00:01:22.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,So we have the total variation. We see it is diminishing all the time.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:22.000,00:01:26.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,But over this region, when these oscillations are created,
Dialogue: 0,00:01:26.000,00:01:28.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,you get a lot of total variation.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:29.000,00:01:31.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,Out of nothing, right?
Dialogue: 0,00:01:31.000,00:01:34.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,So this is a problem we need to address.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:34.000,00:01:38.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,And this is a particular problem about the central flux scheme.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:38.000,00:01:43.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,And the reason for that is we can do a different analysis
Dialogue: 0,00:01:43.000,00:01:46.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,about the central flux scheme
Dialogue: 0,00:01:46.000,00:01:54.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,where the du bar dt
Dialogue: 0,00:01:54.000,00:01:58.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,is equal to 1 over delta x.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:59.000,00:02:06.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,times f that's basically
Dialogue: 0,00:02:06.000,00:02:13.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,half of f plus f plus 1 minus
Dialogue: 0,00:02:13.000,00:02:22.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,oh, this is f plus f minus 1, right?
Dialogue: 0,00:02:22.000,00:02:27.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,minus half of f plus f plus 1.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:29.000,00:02:34.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,So this f gets cancelled with this f here.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:34.000,00:02:37.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,So we have 1 over delta x.
