Dialogue: 0,00:04:43.000,00:04:45.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,over 4 delta x.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:45.000,00:04:47.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:47.000,00:04:49.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,00:04:49.000,00:04:51.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,this number is exactly
