Dialogue: 0,00:05:41.000,00:05:46.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,u i 1 plus 1 square bar 4 delta x.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:46.000,00:05:47.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,We don't get any summation
Dialogue: 0,00:05:47.000,00:05:48.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,on the right hand side
Dialogue: 0,00:05:48.000,00:05:49.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,because all the interiors
Dialogue: 0,00:05:49.000,00:05:50.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,once gets cancelled.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:50.000,00:05:51.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:52.000,00:05:53.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,00:05:53.000,00:05:54.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,if you look at here,
Dialogue: 0,00:05:54.000,00:05:55.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,I have to do,
