Dialogue: 0,00:06:03.000,00:06:07.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,The u i bar cube
Dialogue: 0,00:06:07.000,00:06:10.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,satisfy a certain conservation law
Dialogue: 0,00:06:10.000,00:06:11.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,discreetly.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:11.000,00:06:12.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:12.000,00:06:13.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,00:06:13.000,00:06:14.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,which means
