Dialogue: 0,00:06:22.000,00:06:25.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,the total amount of u cubed
Dialogue: 0,00:06:25.000,00:06:27.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,over these indices
Dialogue: 0,00:06:27.000,00:06:29.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,stays conserved.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:29.000,00:06:31.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,The time derivative is
