Dialogue: 0,00:06:58.000,00:07:00.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,where we don't have any boundaries.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:00.000,00:07:01.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,00:07:01.000,00:07:06.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,if I have periodic domain
Dialogue: 0,00:07:06.000,00:07:10.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,and if the summation over all,
