Dialogue: 0,00:07:24.000,00:07:26.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,because all these things cancel
Dialogue: 0,00:07:26.000,00:07:28.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,over a periodic domain.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:28.000,00:07:30.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,So, I have exact conservation of
